21 (e) "Department" means the department of insurance and
22 financial services.
23 (f) "Director" means the director of the department or the
24 director's designee.
25 (g) (d) "Home improvement loan" means a secured or unsecured
26 loan used for the purpose of repairing, rehabilitating, or
27 remodeling an existing residential dwelling designed for occupancy
